result.formatted_address: 665 King's Rd, North Point, Hong Kong
result.name: Harbour Plaza North Point

reviews.text: Love this place.  Come back to this hotel every summer with my family. Really good service and I really like the decor.

Situated on North Point, Hong Kong Island. Home for a week and not too disappointed. About an hour from the airport. Just across the road from Quarry Bay MTR.
Friendly and helpful staff though English isn't the number one language. Big clean rooms, UK electrical sockets, bar, swimming pool, gym but laundry room for guests in apartments only. 
Recommended.

The staff at reception where not friendly at all.  Being in a different country on the first day you want to feel welcomed but we were not. We were in a thirteen hour flight and when we got to the hotel our rooms were not ready, we had to wait for a further two hours. The rest of our stay was fine.
Great hotel. Close to the subway and takeaway places. Starbucks is right across the road. Very efficient staff.
The price here is relatively cheap. It's close to the MTR station. Good.

reviews.text: 객실내 와이파이 됩니다. 키를 종이카드에 끼워서 주는데 종이카드에 적힌 번호를 치면 와이파이 사용가능해요! 성인6명이라 방2개에 엑스트라베드2개 추가했는데 방 입구가 서로 다른데 방이 이어져 있는 약간 특이한 스위트룸을 주셔서 편하게 사용했네요. 무엇보다도 숙소에서 신호등 하나만 건너면 쿼리베이역이 나와서 너무 편합니다. 트램도 다닙니다. 또 바로 앞에 마켓플레이스(슈퍼), 스타벅스, 서브웨이, 피자헛, 세븐일레븐, 맥심?식당과 빵집이 있어요. 조금 더 걸어가면 맥도날드도 있어요! 중심지에서 멀다고 생각할 수도 있지만 센트럴역까지 금방 가요. 직원분들도 친절하시고 청소도 깨끗하게 잘 해주셔요. 그리고 추울때 히터 요청하면 갖다줘요. 가성비 좋은 호텔 찾으신다면 추천합니다.
가성비가 좋고 뷰도 좋아요 수영장도 깨끗하고 넓어요 수영장 시간은 7시부터 저녁 9시까지입니다. 에어컨이 빵빵합니다 단점을 하나 꼽자면 욕실 환풍기가 거의 죽어가는 수준이라 샤워를 하면 습기가 실내로 다 옮겨가서 엄청 습해져요 꼭 문을 닫고 샤워를 하시길

reviews.text: I came to Greens Cafe during the lunchtime buffet period. The selection is typical of that of mid to high end Hong Kong Island hotels. There is sushi, salad, and a noodle bar along with various dessert options. Overall, expectations were good and in line with the price of the hotel offerings, exact details of which I can't really share because I was treated for lunch that day.
酒店餐廳，坐位舒適，部份有海景，消费不低，自助餐食品中等。
以酒店自助餐的價錢論，它所提供的餐飲環境和食物質素是值回票價的，有時還會有意外之喜。但它的中午散餐選擇少，而且質素不是太好。
想食自坐餐，又唔想出東區，呢度好過無啦
